data.description: Beautifully updated brick home situated on secluded 6.77 acre property. The kitchen features desired upgrades such as quartz countertops and ample cabinet space. Updates to the lighting have been made throughout the house. The property features a 24x50 heated & cooled workshop with kitchen, laundry, 1/2 bath, and a 10ft garage door. There are RV hookups with separate septic tanks for home, workshop, & RV. Radon system installed with transferrable warranty. Features 2-car garage on main floor with 1-car in the basement, all with openers. 25x25 carport with closed sides & 10x25 workshop. New gutters have been installed to front of house. 2 wells located on property. Storm shelter in basement.
